==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dardanelles
<hw>Dardanelles</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>the strait between
the Aegean and the Sea of Marmara that separates European from Asian
Turkey.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Hellespont.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>the unsuccessful campaign in World War I (1915) by
the English and French to open a passage for aid to Russia; defeated by
the Turks.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Dardanelles campaign.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dardanian</ent>⟦br⟧
